  <div class="row">
    <div class="col s2 grey lighten-5">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
          <h5>Documentation</h5>
          <a href="#doc">Getting Started</a>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
          <h5>Users</h5>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="#getusers">/api/v1/users</a></li>
            <li><a href="#getuser">/api/v1/users/:username</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
          <h5>Companies</h5>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="#getcompanies">/api/v1/companies</a></li>
            <li><a href="#getcompany">/api/v1/companies/:name</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s7 grey lighten-5">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section" id="doc">
          <blockquote>
              <h5>Getting Started with DevHub API</h5>
          </blockquote>
          <p>This page will help you get started with DevHub API. You'll be up and running in a jiffy!</p>
          <p>Welcome to the DevHub API (Closed Beta)! We're excited to start giving people access to
            the data on DevHub. Our API has two main sets of endpoints: Users and Companies. Users are
            defined as Github users. Companies are defined as companies.
            To request your access token to the DevHub API just login here.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="getuser">
          <blockquote>
            <h5>/api/v1/users</h5>
            <p>Get all users</p>
          </blockquote>
          <div class="card grey lighten-3">
            <div class="card-content black-text">
                <span class="card-title">Header</span>
                <p>send token</p>
                <span class="card-title">Body</span>
                <p>no params or body is required</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-action">
              <button class="btn waves-effect waves-light" type="submit" name="action">Try It!
               <i class="material-icons right">send</i>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="getusers">
          <blockquote>
            <h5>/api/v1/users/:username</h5>
            <p>Get user by specifying the username of the user</p>
          </blockquote>
          <div class="card grey lighten-3">
            <div class="card-content black-text" id="getuserbtncard">
                <table>
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th data-field="id">Parameter</th>
                        <th data-field="name">Value</th>
                        <th data-field="name">Description</th>
                        <th data-field="price">Data Type</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                   <tr>
                     <td>username</td>
                     <td>
                       <div class="input-field col s12">
                        <input id="getuserbtnfield" type="text" class="validate">
                        <label for="password" data-error="please enter a value">Value</label>
                      </div>
                     </td>
                     <td>github username</td>
                     <td>String</td>
                   </tr>
                 </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="card-action" id="getuserbtnload">
              <button class="btn waves-effect waves-light" id="getuserbtn" type="submit" name="action">Try It!
               <i class="material-icons right">send</i>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s3 grey darken-3">
      <div class="container">
        asdas
      </div>
    </div>
